  "title": "s-dr-073-capacity-exhaustion-permanent-lock",
  "scenario-purpose": "Demonstrate Finding 3 (capacity exhaustion): coordinated dispute flood overwhelms a single-resolver system. 3 escrows exist with the same resolver (capacity=2). First 2 disputes succeed, 3rd raise_dispute is rejected. Funds remain permanently locked in the third escrow with no on-chain recourse \u2014 the escrow exists but no dispute can be opened.",
